Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7201466508632187e-17, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.656321550332976e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"a different level\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"a chilly autumnal morning\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has opened a lot of doors for me.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"doors\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has created more empowerment for the youth back in the country, back in the African continent, because now a lot of youth want to engage in sporting activities, not just athletics, because I have shown them that anything is possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more empowerment\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"the youth\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the African continent\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"youth\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting activities\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"not just athletics\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Letsile Tebogo is building on the legacy of Frankie Fredericks, considered the trailblazer for modern African sprinters.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frankie Fredericks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frankie_Fredericks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the trailblazer\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"modern African sprinters\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he has already gone a step further than the Namibian, who had to settle for silver medals at the 1992 and 1996 Olympics, and he hopes his success can inspire others.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Namibian\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"silver medals\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1992 and 1996 Olympics\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"his success\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I believe there is true potential in Africa, just that we do not have as many resources as other countries,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"true potential\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"as many resources\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So if we have the resources, then Africa could be one of the deadliest continents.\\\"\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadliest continents\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo wants public money to go towards training coaches, improving facilities and stadiums to encourage young athletes.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"training coaches\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"facilities\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"stadiums\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"young athletes\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once you find a gem in Africa, you do not know when you are going to find the next gem,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gem\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"the next gem\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because we have the talent, but we do not have the coaches.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the talent\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That could help us nurture that talent into something very big.\\\"\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"that talent\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Botswana erupted in celebration after Tebogo's success in Paris, with then president Mokgweetsi Masisi declaring a half-day public holiday, and he was given two houses by the government.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{